---
layout: base.njk
title: Forgotten Industries
description: An archive and evidence-based memoir that explores what happens to the things we leave behind; abandoned places, unfinished projects, deserted machines, and the parts of ourselves we once thought lost.
canonical: https://forgotten-industries.net/
---

<section class="masthead">
  <div class="section-inner masthead-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Archive & evidence-based memoir / established MMXIV</p>
      <h1 class="sr-only">{{ site.name }}</h1>
      <p class="tagline">{{ site.tagline }}</p>
    </div>
    <img class="hero-image" src="/assets/forgotten-industries.jpeg" alt="Forgotten Industries logo, EST MMXIV">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="mirror-band" aria-labelledby="mirror-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Figure 1</p>
      <h2 id="mirror-heading">Seven routes. One archive map.</h2>
    </div>

    <div>
      <ul class="ledger" aria-label="Archive routes">
        {% for item in site.nav %}
        <li class="ledger-item">
          <a class="ledger-header-link" href="{{ item.href }}">
            <span class="ledger-label">{{ item.french or item.label }}</span>
            {% if item.english %}
            <span class="ledger-translation-line">
              <span class="ledger-rail" aria-hidden="true">//</span>
              <span class="ledger-translation">{{ item.english }}</span>
              <span class="ledger-rail" aria-hidden="true">//</span>
            </span>
            {% endif %}
          </a>
          <p class="ledger-summary">{{ item.summary }}</p>
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>

      <div class="stats" aria-label="Archive counts">
        <a class="stat" href="/archive/projects/">
          <strong>{{ archive.projects | count }}</strong>
          <span>Projects</span>
        </a>
        <a class="stat" href="/archive/inventory/">
          <strong>{{ archive.inventory | count }}</strong>
          <span>Inventory records</span>
        </a>
        <a class="stat" href="/archive/field-logs/">
          <strong>{{ archive.fieldLogs | count }}</strong>
          <span>Field logs</span>
        </a>
        <a class="stat" href="/archive/social-evidence/">
          <strong>{{ archive.socialPosts | count }}</strong>
          <span>Social evidence</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band" aria-labelledby="featured-lanes-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="mx-auto w-[min(760px,100%)] py-8">
      <p class="section-label">Public Spine</p>
      <h2 id="featured-lanes-heading">Entry 000 stays first.</h2>

      <p class="stamp-row mt-6" aria-label="Entry status">
        <span class="stamp">Manuscripts</span>
        <span class="stamp stamp-muted">Entry 000</span>
      </p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/2026-06-06-prelude-a-thing-documented-is-a-thing-not-yet-lost.html">A Thing Documented Is a Thing Not Yet Lost</a>
      </h3>
      <p class="entry-note">Entry 000 / long-form origin manuscript</p>

      <h3 class="mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/2026-06-10-perspective-peregrines-and-pang.html">Perspective, Peregrines, &amp; “Pang”</a>
      </h3>
      <p class="entry-note">Entry 001 / first field doctrine</p>

      <p class="entry-note mt-4">
        <a href="/posts/index.html">View all curated posts</a>
      </p>

      <ul class="lane-list mt-8" aria-label="Public lane highlights">
        <li>
          <a class="panel-link" href="/hang-on-to-each-other/">
            <span>Manuals</span>
            <h3>Hang On To Each Other</h3>
            <p>Manual 001: recovered CaseLabs Mercury S8 assembly reference and living instruction shelf.</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="panel-link" href="/en-direct/">
            <span>En Direct</span>
            <h3>Live channel split</h3>
            <p>One route for two short-form streams: Bluesky field notes and authored daily field logs.</p>
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a class="panel-link" href="/projects/">
            <span>Projects</span>
            <h3>Dossiers and continuity</h3>
            <p>Long-running systems, object records, and project context packets that keep the archive coherent.</p>
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="field-notes-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Field Notes / Field Logs</p>
      <h2 id="field-notes-heading">Two short-form channels, different sources.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <h3>Signal Split</h3>
      <p>Field Notes are imported from Bluesky. Field Logs are authored daily notes: shorter writings, process fragments, and bench records that do not need a full essay yet.</p>
      <p class="action-row"><a href="/field-notes/">Open Field Notes</a> / <a href="/field-logs/">Open Field Logs</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="source-band" aria-labelledby="shelves-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Shelves</p>
      <h2 id="shelves-heading">The site spine is an archive map.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="shelf-list">
      {% for shelf in site.shelves %}
      <li>
        <h3 id="{{ shelf.slug }}">{% if shelf.href %}<a href="{{ shelf.href }}">{{ shelf.label }}</a>{% else %}{{ shelf.label }}{% endif %}</h3>
        <p>{{ shelf.purpose }}</p>
        <p class="shelf-note">{{ shelf.tone }} {{ shelf.note }}</p>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="evidence-band" aria-labelledby="evidence-heading">
  <div class="section-inner band-grid">
    <div>
      <p class="section-label">Evidence</p>
      <h2 id="evidence-heading">Raw shelves remain visible.</h2>
    </div>

    <ul class="link-list">
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/archive.html">L'Archive</a></h3>
        <p>The generated master record for posts, inventory, dossiers, field logs, source sets, and preserved evidence.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/inventory.html">Inventory</a></h3>
        <p>Canonical machine, part, accessory, condition, and disposition records.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/social-posts.html">Imported social evidence</a></h3>
        <p>Recovered Tumblr and Instagram posts with local media and Markdown sources.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/dist/forgotten-industries.json">Generated archive JSON</a></h3>
        <p>Machine-readable output generated from the source YAML.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/site-snapshots/github-pages-trial-2026-06-06/index.html">Stowed GitHub Pages trial snapshot</a></h3>
        <p>The pre-reset static surface preserved as evidence, not discarded history.</p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <h3><a href="/docs/process/2026-06-07-public-spine-and-manual-shelf.md">Process record</a></h3>
        <p>The public spine, manual shelf, and design-language decisions documented as part of the archive itself.</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
